OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,FCornwall's MPs are celebrating as the
OL,7,Fgovernment looks set to scrap plans
OL,8,Ffor a shared mayor with Devon.
OL,10,FIn a letter sent to MPs, and seen by
OL,11,FITV West Country, the Secretary of
OL,12,FState for Housing, Communities and
OL,13,FLocal Government said Cornwall Council
OL,14,Fis likely to be designated a Single
OL,15,FFoundation Strategic Authority.
OL,17,FSteve Reed told politicians, including
OL,18,Fthe Council's leader, that a bespoke
OL,19,Fdeal would be "in recognition of
OL,20,FCornwall's distinct local identity"
OL,21,Fand "unique status".
