OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,FIt would end the long-running debate
OL,7,Fover whether Devon and Cornwall should
OL,8,Felect a join mayor, something Labour
OL,9,Fpoliticians to the east of the Tamar
OL,10,Fhave been campaigning for since the
OL,11,FParty took office in 2024.
OL,13,FUnder the government's plans to push
OL,14,Fpower and money out of Westminster,
OL,15,Felected mayors will be given the
OL,16,Fauthority to have more of a say over
OL,17,Fthings like local transport, housing
OL,18,Fand jobs. Effectively, mayors are seen
OL,19,Fas increasingly important for
OL,20,Fdelivering the objectives of this
OL,21,FLabour government.
