OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,FIn Devon and Cornwall, the
OL,7,Fgovernment's preference was to see the
OL,8,Ftwo merge and elect a mayor. "I think
OL,9,Fthat's the best opportunity," said
OL,10,FDefence Minister and Plymouth Sutton
OL,11,Fand Devonport MP, Luke Pollard,
OL,12,Fearlier this year.
OL,14,F"I'm still proud to be a Janner.
OL,15,FPeople from Cornwall will still be
OL,16,Fproud to be from Cornwall, but we will
OL,17,Fhave more powers to shape our future."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
