OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,FCornwall's MPs have, on the whole,
OL,7,Fdisagreed, with one Labour MP telling
OL,8,FITV he was willing to rebel against
OL,9,Fhis government if it it forced a
OL,10,Fcombined mayor on the far South West.
OL,12,FPerran Moon, Labour's MP for Camborne
OL,13,Fand Redruth, said he was "thrilled" at
OL,14,Fthe prospect of a bespoke deal, which
OL,15,Falso came with a promise that the
OL,16,Fgovernment will request with the
OL,17,FCouncil of Europe to increase the UK's
OL,18,Fformal recognition of the Cornish
OL,19,Flanguage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
