OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,FNoah Law, Labour MP for St Austell and
OL,7,FNewquay, said: "The need for
OL,8,Fdevolution in Cornwall on a Single
OL,9,FFoundation geographic basis is a
OL,10,Fmatter of broad political consensus
OL,11,Fand is something which I have been
OL,12,Fpushing for from day one, along with
OL,13,Fthe powers and investment needed to
OL,14,Frealise Cornwall's potential.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
