OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,F"I'm delighted to see that, despite
OL,7,Fall the claims that this couldn't be
OL,8,Fdone, or some wider South West Mayor
OL,9,Fwas inevitable, our Labour Government
OL,10,Frecognises Cornwall's right to define
OL,11,Fits own future, together with more
OL,12,Finvestment on the way in the form of
OL,13,FFair Funding and the establishment of
OL,14,Fa publicly-owned investment fund for
OL,15,FCornish industries."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
