OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,FSimilarly, Cornwall's Lib Dem MPs
OL,7,Fwelcomed the news. "For months I've
OL,8,Fbeen calling on Ministers to respect
OL,9,FCornwall's identity and reject any
OL,10,Fplan to merge us into a wider Devon
OL,11,Fand Cornwall authority," said Ben
OL,12,FMaguire.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
