OL,3,CCornwall MPs 'celebrating' as plan for
OL,4,Cjoint mayor with Devon scrapped
OL,6,F"Though of course welcome, this is
OL,7,Fjust a step on the road to Cornwall
OL,8,Fhaving far greater say in the future
OL,9,Fshaping of our services and
OL,10,Fcommunities. We're not motivated to
OL,11,Fcut ourselves off, but to cut Cornwall
OL,12,Finto the celebration of diversity,
OL,13,Fboth here in the UK and a wider
OL,14,Fworld," said Andrew George.
OL,16,F"I must congratulate all of my Cornish
OL,17,FMP colleagues. We stuck together and
OL,18,Fmade it clear we wouldn't lie down and
OL,19,Faccept the government's original
OL,20,Foffer."
